  <h5><m>dèan</m> in lexicalised verb expressions</h5>
  <p><b>dèan</b> + <a href="?xx=adjectives/adjectives">adjective</a> –</p>
  <ul>
    <li><i>sleamhainn</i>
      <en>slippery</en> ⇒ <m>dèan sleamhainn</m>
      <en>lubricate</en></li>
  </ul>
